subject: Tennis
United States Open (Tennis)
lead_paragraph: Severine Bremond, a 2006 Wimbledon quarterfinalist, and the former United States Fed Cup players Jamea Jackson and Ahsha Rolle were among seven women awarded wild-card entries into the United States Open by the United States Tennis Association.
